channel.title: Help!
channel.description:
:confused:
What am i supposed to do??? Every time i try to log in, a message says:
Error connecting to server.Must be down.Click "Cancel" then "Start server" to make your own.
OR
No response from server. Please choose another world.
Whats wrong???(This happens EVERY TIME i try to log in)
BTW, im still new here...sooo i really think i need a little help...
Thanks.
